{"tid":2297309,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網上驚現售賣「確診唾液樣本」　賣家：即買即賺$4,500","createTime":"2020-11-23T07:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T07:50:24.000Z","uid":28114,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"65509e59eaa796b2a5048689cd416a9e0c95d767","tid":2297309,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T07:32:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/11/23/5000/fun-tech/?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F11%2F23%2F5000%2Ffun-tech%2F%3F&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUndkum%2F%2B3HP0Ta45uqRfUpIg%3D&h=a3c7fea2\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/11/23/5000/fun-tech/?</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/mfile_1544543_1_20200819072555-1280x625.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2Fmfile_1544543_1_20200819072555-1280x625.jpg&h=de571641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府昨日（22 日）宣布，將會向確診肺炎者派發港幣 $5,000 津貼，不過，不少手網民質疑政府做法，指政府變相「鼓勵」大家中招，更有網民在網上討論區發文，指確診者可兜售確診口水「互惠互利」，而一些拍賣交易平台以及 Facebook 群組<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局局長陳肇始昨日（22 日）指，部分基層市民因怕確診後手停口停，對強制檢測卻步，故政府決定向確診者派發 $5,000 以鼓勵其參與檢測，不過，相關做法惹來不少爭議，不少網上討論區均有人發文指要以千元徵收確診者口水，以諷刺政府做法。<br />\n<br />\n而一些拍賣交易平台以及 Facebook 群組亦有人開始「兜售」確診口水，叫價 $500 至 $2,500，部份更強調只要扣除買樣本的成本後，政府津貼可「淨賺」$4,500。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_4240-1-e1606107292724-1007x2048.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2FIMG_4240-1-e1606107292724-1007x2048.png&h=04e6e14c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/IMG_4241-e1606102724170.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2FIMG_4241-e1606102724170.jpg&h=f25b1541&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然坊間對此做法負評居多，但陳肇始今早（23 日）再接受港台節目訪問時就指相關做法獲專家支持，不過，除市民對此做法有疑慮，議員亦有其他意見，如鄺俊宇、何君堯等均有在其 Facebook 發表對此做法的個人見解。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-11-23-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%8812.05.09.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-11-23-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%258812.05.09.png&h=9d35bafa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-11-23-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%8812.03.37.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-11-23-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%258812.03.37.png&h=59875e4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61a707c170b56407d67e6723ea572ba8b4eec7b2","tid":2297309,"uid":275498,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T07:33:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">玩膠既小心玩到畀狗吠 <br />\n<br />\n政府班狗永遠無錯<br />\n錯既係玩膠既人 </span></strong>"},{"pid":"b882c87bc9b2a2c79d2bce1ab17b7543b112719d","tid":2297309,"uid":35514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T07:34:41.000Z","msg":"買咗陰性口水有無得去投訴商品說明條例？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af50005886951e6577caf709099b26489ae7bdbf","tid":2297309,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"61a707c170b56407d67e6723ea572ba8b4eec7b2","tid":2297309,"uid":275498,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T07:33:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">玩膠既小心玩到畀狗吠 <br />\n<br />\n政府班狗永遠無錯<br />\n錯既係玩膠既人 </span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T07:36:14.000Z","msg":"用幽默方式戲謔有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce35fc33bde3dcd06855f3e636224beab2b1141","tid":2297309,"uid":239270,"like":0,"disli